Skill: frenzy!     Timer: Damage       GL: 14    Cost: 120

An experienced fighter may work himself into a killing frenzy where
he is able to fire off a quick succession of blows at everything in the room
for a short period of time. Be forewarned that your foes will recover very
quickly and may strike a fatal blow before you finish this maneuver.

You must already be in combat to attempt a frenzy!

Syntax is: frenzy!
